Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是难得的新部员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得太普通会被认为很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我会这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有律这样想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快画啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我自己画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长她们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来了  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  叫她小律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我唯就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没错  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想看着可爱的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好干…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能眨眼竟然这么痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个社团真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪是扮姐姐啊  是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？  完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过了吗  要拍得像全家福一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家福？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这就是中野梓的入部纪念了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家笑一个～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入部纪念吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  高三今天不是已经没课了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有很重要的东西要送过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个之前玩过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的婆婆给了我八朔橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿吃的东西来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业照？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我说今天样本会送到  大家就说要到学校来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像无论如何都想看一下的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看了  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打开了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么额头在发光啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我拍得很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么用这张照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我选的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们  比起那个  那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再拿吃的东西玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯拍得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得很有小唯的感觉  很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有我的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说像小孩子一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太直接了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  和和  这个还只是样本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  把相机拿来  我要重拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  一定要用正规的相机拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拿正规的相机来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照顾每个人的意见的话  就没完没了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  这可不是普通的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毕业照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直流传下去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过个100年也会被保留着的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆的同学的刘海好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…会变成那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗  让人家留下了深刻的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐是有点任性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和也真坚决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  现在有件伤脑筋的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是佐和子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是要她今天检查好后  明天就送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是说不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为感冒请假了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶  整人成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小佐和竟然会感冒  真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小佐和检查也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  如果小佐和说这照片要换的话就会换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为此而检查的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片应该换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换张更可爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:06:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以拜托你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  因为是我们的毕业照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平时要有干劲啊  唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上也能猜出她在打什么主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人生活的老师的房间～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有个激动不已的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能看到老师的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  梓就努力上好下午的课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后  音乐教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没什么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没别的路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  乖乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别和它搞得这么热乎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老师的家离得不是很远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么近的话就能睡到8点多了  真是幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象的要普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为小佐和的家一定会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘等着你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么家啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊  澪同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…就这样去会不会给她添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒吗  一个人一定很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的东西也买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总会有隐私的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐私？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男…男朋友在  之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  403室的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有点紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要按咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这里是405！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没人在家啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中要有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像在警戒着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在邻居都不在  出来也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行公务！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家不缺东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏他已经暴露了  束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师已经被完全包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您母亲在哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷偷摸摸在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在隐藏什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是垃圾啊  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很麻烦  就想要不要就这身打扮去扔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒谎了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就能蒙混…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扰民了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打听了我的住所？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是特地来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是小小的感冒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有件非常重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情？  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～也不算什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那明天再说也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  今天打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还没定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定了就告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么样都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4  5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面也挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都没有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没劲儿～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不住你们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想得那么严重  我们也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯  那么开始调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了  其实我一直睡到中午才起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因此烧也退了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现小佐和过去的衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦～好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看温度又要上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  小佐和的毕业相册
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照片蛮好看的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说来您看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你说的重要事情  就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和正在发愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就拿来老师这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  稍微等下  我现在检查一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  请问～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我觉得有张照片也许换一下可能比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  哪张哪张？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…  是这个叫做平泽唯同学的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看额头这里有点不太对头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗？挺可爱的嘛  很像你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看唯的肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什什什什什什么啊？！这照片！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是看错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这里确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么时候拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我记得是修学旅行之前一段时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么久的事情…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这张照片就换一下好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚想起什么事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？没…没想到啥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…这个…其实…这事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是对不住你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太对不住你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就不换了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那老师检查剩下照片的时候我们来做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顺便也帮忙打扫和洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也想做饭～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也比较倾向下厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！那我们猜拳决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦  猜拳决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那倒也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是石头  石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次  一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我赢啊！给我赢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了！胜利的剪刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯  让你们见识下我的真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你不用那么干劲满满啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  先准备一合大米…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一合是多少公斤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一合相当于中文里一升的1/10）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  随便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天还能去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师吗  不好意思突然打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐她们还在您那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呢  你要不要也过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好在做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个  这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们暂时还会留在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐她们还在老师家里  应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得倒也不用这么偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我会担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让她们看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  不努力点的话我会把光脚的照片放到毕业相册上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  杯子稍微往右点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会变安静了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现黑色内衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你在孤零零生病  还专门带大家来看你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  一起吃了饭再走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还要回学校一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里挤九个人也有点小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来你们已经毕业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今年三月  我们考上同一所大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那轻音部明年怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说又准备废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少成员？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在帮我们圆场吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看她一副自信十足的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有希望加入的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会以为我们明年会继续留在轻音部啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是你  怎么可能会搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是注定留级了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是她没说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梓喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续一会吧  学姐她们还没回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小佐和老师是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新欢演奏会上还要多演奏一首吧  不努力点怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙练习也蛮有趣  我完全没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍她们练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑…跑啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  学姐  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新欢演奏会  好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这次我慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯你跳得早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下张就不改了  我要回办公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一～二」就跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  你也练习一下比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都没失败过  别担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳慢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去海边  而是要去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部打算去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想去海外
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where very delicious cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  姐姐你们居然要去海外…我稍微有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where my hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去海外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.48,0:24:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去英国看演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国
